Initial report

2022-11-04

Response rate

We invited the ALSPAC mailing list to participate, which included 1148 email addresses, of which 54 bounced, leaving 1094 emails. The survey was completed 107 times and partially completed 18 times. This gives a response rate for completed surveys of 10% and a response rate for any questions 11%.

The median time taken for complete survey responses was 7.2 minutes (IQR: 4.3 - 13.1)
